journEZ

journEZ is a a travel website that allows users to easily create trips and organize their trip itineraries and costs all from one platform. This was created via the MERN + graphQL stack.

{/* SOCIAL NETWORK THOUGHTS*/}
social-network- thoughts

Social network thoughts is a simple social media website that allows users to exchange thoughts and comments with other registered users. This was created via the MERN + graphQL stack.
